#. Tag: glossterm
#: index.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid "DCOP"
msgstr "DCOP"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<acronym>DCOP</acronym>, which stands for Desktop COmmunication Protocol, is "
"a light-weight interprocess and software componentry communication system "
"used in &kde; 3. Replaced with &DBus; in &kde; SC 4.&newpara; More info:"
"&newpara; &linkstart;\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/DCOP\"&linkmid;"
"Wikipedia: DCOP&linkend;"
msgstr ""
"<acronym>DCOP</acronym>, qui signifie Desktop COmmunication Protocol, est un "
"système de communication inter-processus et composants systèmes léger "
"utilisé par &kde; 3. Remplacé par &DBus; dans &kde; SC 4.&newpara; Plus "
"d'informations :&newpara; &linkstart;\"https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/DCOP"
"\"&linkmid;Wikipedia: DCOP&linkend;"

