msgid "Kross"
msgstr "Kross"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:530
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Kross is a scripting framework, enabling support for multiple scripting "
"languages. A plugin system allows for the support of further languages in "
"the future."
msgstr ""
"Kross est un framework de scripts, permettant la gestion de plusieurs "
"langages de scripts. Un système de modules pour la gestion de davantage de "
"langages à l'avenir."

